#### Priority Algorithm (Frontend Implementation)

\\\javascript
calculatePriorityScore(notification) {
    // Type-based weights
    const typeWeight = WEIGHTS[notification.Type] || 0; // Placement=3, Result=2, Event=1
    
    // Time decay calculation
    const timestamp = new Date(notification.Timestamp);
    const now = new Date();
    const ageMs = now.getTime() - timestamp.getTime();
    const ageHours = ageMs / (1000 * 60 * 60);
    const maxAgeHours = 7 * 24;
    const recencyScore = Math.max(0, 100 * (1 - ageHours / maxAgeHours));
    
    // Final score
    return (typeWeight * 100) + recencyScore;
}

Sorting:
1. Primary: Priority score (descending)
2. Secondary: Timestamp (newest first)
